ABBOTT v. WARDEN OF THE MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 137,

September Term, 1963.]

Decided April 17, 1964.

Before Henderson, Hammond, Prescott, Marbury and Sybert, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal from a denial of post con*634viction relief is denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of the court below. .
